{"baseRefName":"main","body":"Fixes #1645\n\n## Summary\n\n- Fixed `--auto-restart-until-mergeable` readiness comment deduplication for pull requests with more than one page of conversation comments.\n- Added a regression test that reproduces PR 1643's failure mode: a stale `Ready to merge` comment on page 1 and the latest session-ending log on page 2.\n- Added the issue case study, raw GitHub data, and downloaded execution logs under `docs/case-studies/issue-1645`.\n- Added a patch changeset for the CLI behavior fix.\n- Merged the latest `main` into the issue branch and preserved both upstream tests and the issue 1645 regression in `npm test`.\n\n## Root Cause\n\n`checkForExistingComment()` fetched PR comments through `gh api .../issues/{pr}/comments --jq '[.[].body]'` without `--paginate`.\n\nFor PR 1643, the thread had 33 conversation comments. GitHub CLI returned only the default first page of 30 comments, so deduplication found an older session-ending log at index 27 and an older `Ready to merge` comment at index 28. The real final session-ending log was comment index 32 on page 2, so the helper incorrectly skipped the final readiness comment.\n\nThe fix adds `--paginate` to the comment query before applying the existing session-scoped duplicate check.\n\n## Case Study\n\nInvestigation details, saved artifacts, timeline, external references, and fix plan are documented here:\n\nhttps://github.com/link-assistant/hive-mind/blob/issue-1645-53daead64de1/docs/case-studies/issue-1645/README.md\n\n## Verification\n\n- `node tests/test-ready-to-merge-pagination-1645.mjs`\n- `node --check src/solve.auto-merge-helpers.lib.mjs`\n- `node --check tests/test-ready-to-merge-pagination-1645.mjs`\n- `npm test`\n- `npm run lint`\n- `npm run format:check`\n- `node tests/docs-validation.mjs`\n- `node scripts/validate-changeset.mjs`\n- `bash scripts/check-mjs-syntax.sh`\n- `bash scripts/check-file-line-limits.sh`\n- `npm run check:duplication`\n- `git diff origin/main...HEAD --check`\n\nScreenshots are not applicable; this is backend CLI behavior.\n","commits":[{"authoredDate":"2026-04-18T22:37:31Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-04-18T22:37:31Z","messageBody":"Adding .gitkeep for PR creation (default mode).\nThis file will be removed when the task is complete.\n\nIssue: https://github.com/link-assistant/hive-mind/issues/1645","messageHeadline":"Initial commit with task details","oid":"e3f344920b7ccac94e69b10ce8b9d563a40d6715"},{"authoredDate":"2026-04-18T22:55:22Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-04-18T22:55:22Z","messageBody":"","messageHeadline":"fix(auto-merge): paginate ready comment lookup","oid":"12f57618981e2bd689f3fddb00c76b955eda946b"},{"authoredDate":"2026-04-18T22:59:02Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-04-18T22:59:02Z","messageBody":"","messageHeadline":"merge main into issue branch","oid":"3293624ebe73effa1431406cc54e090824597e22"},{"authoredDate":"2026-04-18T22:59:33Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-04-18T22:59:33Z","messageBody":"","messageHeadline":"chore: drop branch setup marker","oid":"24785cc94773f0528440f345a23b37f42c9f0586"}],"headRefName":"issue-1645-53daead64de1","isDraft":true,"number":1646,"reviewDecision":"","state":"OPEN","statusCheckRollup":[{"__typename":"CheckRun","completedAt":"2026-04-18T23:00:10Z","conclusion":"SUCCESS","detailsUrl":"https://github.com/link-assistant/hive-mind/actions/runs/24615832960/job/71977756792","name":"detect-changes","startedAt":"2026-04-18T22:59:58Z","status":"COMPLETED","workflowName":"Checks and release"},{"__typename":"CheckRun","completedAt":"2026-04-18T22:59:56Z","conclusion":"SKIPPED","detailsUrl":"htt